title: Luxembourg Gross Household Saving Rate
description: Household Saving Rate in Luxembourg decreased to 18.17 percent in 2021 from 24.22 percent in 2020. Personal Savings in Luxembourg averaged 13.42 percent from 1995 until 2021, reaching an all time high of 24.22 percent in 2020 and a record low of 9.75 percent in 1999. This page provides - Luxembourg Personal Savings - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: EUROSTAT
